                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "Funded in PE 0303131F:\n- Continue planning and initiate integration, analysis, and testing activities for NC3 WS\n- Continue assessment of NC3 WS\n- Develop AF NC3 WS test plans"
                                            }
                                        },
                                        "BudgetYearOne": {
                                            "Funding": {
                                                "val": "12.636"
                                            }
                                        },
                                        "BudgetYearOneBase": {
                                            "Funding": {
                                                "val": "12.636"
                                            },
                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "NC3 weapon system integration efforts including, but not limited to:\n- Implement test and certification program for NC3 WS and expand existing HF testbed utilizing a phased approach\n- Perform NC3 physics, communication and networking analysis\n- Develop and evolve technical framework of the NC3 WS to meet mission threats of 2030 and beyond\n- Conduct WS analysis, develop WS capability model, plan WS updates, and implement WS updates\n- Evaluate options for pacing system-of-system performance improvements within constraints of WS\n- Analyze, model, and prototype emerging NC3 technologies\n- Develop and implement NC3 WS program and materiel management control processes including risk management, configuration control, integrated scheduling, budgeting and cost controls, etc.  \n- Conduct NC3 WS health assessments, reporting, and issue resolution"
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
